{"tid":267327,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普上訴至最高法院　要求恢復回教國家入境禁令","createTime":"2017-06-02T07:58:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-03T07:34:45.000Z","uid":22675,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c38c7cdddf6993e162cbe3d32354a8760c2aaee8","tid":267327,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T07:58:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170602/photo/bknint-20170602122121744-0602_17011_001_01p.jpg?20170602135643\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170602%2Fphoto%2Fbknint-20170602122121744-0602_17011_001_01p.jpg%3F20170602135643&h=c11cd1e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美國總統特朗普政府周四向最高法院提出上訴，要求恢復其頒布的入境禁令，以禁止6個回教國家公民入境。惟禁令極具爭議，遭地方法院封殺執行。<br />\n<br />\n司法部發言人表示，特朗普頒布的行政命令，是在其行政權力範圍內力圖保證國家安全以及保護民眾遠離恐怖主義。發言人又稱，總統無法接受那些支持或庇護恐怖主義的國家的公民入境，除非經審查後確定不會對美國造成安全威脅。<br />\n　　<br />\n特朗普3月6日簽署修改後的新版入境限制行政命令，將伊拉克從原名單上剔除，但仍禁止蘇丹、敍利亞、也門、伊朗、索馬里和利比亞6國公民入境，但在生效前夕，夏威夷及馬里蘭州的聯邦法官先後裁定暫緩執行。司法部其後提出上訴，惟遭駁回。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170602/bknint-20170602122121744-0602_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170602%2Fbknint-20170602122121744-0602_17011_001.html&d=1PqeU65tlB6pUrEWQ1zVbWowyooGr0BEXXUM5gBrg7E%3D&h=fdbef546\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170602/bknint-20170602122121744-0602_17011_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a802876f8179610862c7263ed93ad20f1421c22b","tid":267327,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T08:25:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f9d697c984e30b2cce1607762634f31910128c4","tid":267327,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-03T07:34:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}